<module>
    <h>sinn</h>
    <p><g>sinn</g>
        <en>we, us</en> is the first person plural <a href="?xx=nouns/personal_pronouns">personal
            pronoun</a>.</p>


    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <p><g>sinn</g> can be used as the subject of a verb.</p>
            <p>Examples with <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>
                <en>be</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>sinn</m> trang.</gd>
                        <tr>We are busy.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>sinn</m> trang ag obair.</gd>
                        <tr>We ae busy working.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with other verbs – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Chunnaic <m>sinn</m> iolair mhór an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>We saw a big eagle today..</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9 [226]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>




